  "texts": [
    "One limitation during the labeling stage is that we generated ChatGPT responses first before the experts review and correct to create the ground truth.",
    "While this could introduce potential bias towards ChatGPT, we believed that ground truth is still valid to evaluate other models.",
    "ChatGPT might also not be reliable 100% of the time, as we have seen that it failed to generate responses for a small fraction of the notes.",
    "In production, it is critical to have back-up plans in place such as alternative LLMs to ensure the system can reliably extract scores for all notes.",
    "Additionally, we conducted a large-scale human evaluation for a single dementia use case, prioritizing result reliability over assessing various clinical scenarios."
  ],
